  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826710/extras/c90b1c305f59db805f0311d7c564e084.avif?t=1747964458\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826710/extras_big/c90b1c305f59db805f0311d7c564e084.avif?t=1747964458 width=800 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assemble your dream team by befriending a variety of unique Creatures to fight alongside you in real time. Choose your Creatures wisely to best handle any challenge that stands in your way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826710/extras/49045f0b04fb6d061e87c327b60bc336.poster.avif?t=1747964458\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826710/extras/49045f0b04fb6d061e87c327b60bc336.webm?t=1747964458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826710/extras/49045f0b04fb6d061e87c327b60bc336.mp4?t=1747964458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826710/extras/8ebb0015cca1912dcecdd44fd2f8bfc9.avif?t=1747964458\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826710/extras_big/8ebb0015cca1912dcecdd44fd2f8bfc9.avif?t=1747964458 width=800 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create powerful, diverse, and stylish playstyles through gameplay-altering skill gems, perks, weapons and more while looking the part with tons of hats to dress your Creatures up in.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826710/extras/7f131a31b96f3215e879d1da1b072c76.poster.avif?t=1747964458\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826710/extras/7f131a31b96f3215e879d1da1b072c76.webm?t=1747964458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826710/extras/7f131a31b96f3215e879d1da1b072c76.mp4?t=1747964458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826710/extras/a7cf52c22e64334552897d10a3c4a7dd.avif?t=1747964458\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826710/extras_big/a7cf52c22e64334552897d10a3c4a7dd.avif?t=1747964458 width=800 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your Pocket Garden to grow food and create helpful Connection Bonuses for your Creatures in an engaging organization mini-game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826710/extras/1353b6009e8b0a1fcd8c0c35821da4f1.poster.avif?t=1747964458\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826710/extras/1353b6009e8b0a1fcd8c0c35821da4f1.webm?t=1747964458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826710/extras/1353b6009e8b0a1fcd8c0c35821da4f1.mp4?t=1747964458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826710/extras/d0b65086c5d9ec0c91b127fadbdac239.avif?t=1747964458\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826710/extras_big/d0b65086c5d9ec0c91b127fadbdac239.avif?t=1747964458 width=800 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fill out your Bestiary on the fifty unique Creatures in Thera to unlock powerful buffs and items for your party.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826710/extras/39e1e7cd3fc078b9df84b1c5f40aede5.poster.avif?t=1747964458\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826710/extras/39e1e7cd3fc078b9df84b1c5f40aede5.webm?t=1747964458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826710/extras/39e1e7cd3fc078b9df84b1c5f40aede5.mp4?t=1747964458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826710/extras/db5aa381ccaf40ca9bc8c10aa141df9a.avif?t=1747964458\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826710/extras_big/db5aa381ccaf40ca9bc8c10aa141df9a.avif?t=1747964458 width=800 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the vast world of Thera and all its secrets as you take on your quest of destiny.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" aut